
Customize the Pet Name Generation:

Change Word Count:

To generate names with more words, adjust the length parameter:

hcl
Copy code
length = 3  # e.g., "quirky-happy-panda"
Change Separator:

Use a different separator or remove it:

hcl
Copy code
separator = "_"  # e.g., "bouncy_fluffy_kitten"
Or:

hcl
Copy code
separator = ""   # e.g., "sleepybear"
Set a Prefix or Suffix:

Add a prefix or suffix to the name:

hcl
Copy code
resource "random_pet" "pet_name" {
  length    = 2
  separator = "-"
  prefix    = "pet-"
  suffix    = "-001"
}
Resulting in names like pet-happy-dog-001.

